dataObjects.title: Biology
dataObjects.description: Used for snail control (Ref.4967).  Not confined to any particular type of substrate in Lake Victoria.  Ubiquitous in waters less than 20 m.  Found in papyrus swamps (Ref. 5602).  Omnivorous, swamp-dweller (Ref. 6770).
